title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - Biggest Moments of the Year So Far...with Morgan2 and Raymundo
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - Biggest Moments of the Year So Far...with Morgan2 and Raymundo
description:
This edition of the podcast features behind the scenes from show members and moments that happened after we turned off the microphones. Since it was a holiday weekend, Morgan brings on Raymundo to talk about some of the biggest moments of the year so far.
